summary:
After years of operating as a small hoster, we are expanding business worldwide.
We offer dedicated and virtual hosting appliances, voip, online backup, colocation and ip-transit services throughout 3 different High Tier Datacenters and networks in the Netherlands.

Throughout the African region we deployed DSL subscriptions, and are deploying dedicated and virtual services throughout the francophone regions in Africa.
